!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nEste \u00e9 o m\u00f3dulo base dos recursos humanos brasileiro e implementa adapta\u00e7\u00f5es nos modelos b\u00e1sicos do cadastro de Empregados e suas depend\u00eancias:\n\n- Campo CPF com formata\u00e7\u00e3o e valida\u00e7\u00e3o desto memso;\n- CPTS com valida\u00e7\u00e3o;\n- PIS/PASEF;\n- Certificado de servi\u00e7o militar;\n- Naturalidade;\n- Escolaridade;\n- Dependentes;\n- RG;\n- T\u00edtulo de eleitor;\n- Paternidade;\n- Etinia;\n- Tipo sangu\u00edneo;\n- Incapacidade f\u00edsica;\n- Tipo: Funcion\u00e1rio / Aut\u00f4nomo / Terceirizado / Cedido;\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nEste m\u00f3dulo tem uma depedencia do pacote python erpbrasil.base\n\n## Configuration\n\nEste m\u00f3dulo n\u00e3o requer nenhuma configura\u00e7\u00e3o especial.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_br_hr%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- KMEE\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Rafael Lima\n- Matheus Felix\n- Luis Felipe Mileo \\<<mailto:mileo@kmee.com.br>>\n- Daniel Sadamo Hirayama \\<<mailto:daniel.sadamo@kmee.com.br>>\n- Bianca Bartolomei \\<<mailto:bianca.bartolomei@kmee.com.br>>\n- Hendrix Costa\n- Luis Felipe do Divino\n- Luis Ot\u00e1vio Malta \\<<mailto:luis.malta@kmee.com.br>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-brazil](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/14.0/l10n_br_hr) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent", "documentation": ["(c) 2014 Kmee - Rafael da Silva Lima <rafael.lima@kmee.com.br>", "(c) 2014 Kmee - Matheus Felix <matheus.felix@kmee.com.br>", "(c) 2016 KMEE Inform\u00e1tica - Daniel Sadamo <daniel.sadamo@kmee.com.br>", "License AGPL-3 - See http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent._get_default_employee", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent.create", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "vals", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent.onchange_cpf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_employee_dependent.HrEmployeeDependent._description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_hr.models.hr_